{"tid":2009674,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"港共：停止無謂反抗 否則打壓黃圈飲食業","createTime":"2020-05-10T02:35:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-10T02:53:54.000Z","uid":21470,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"8198b4215965dfb35c792ef77d527078ba7b3e43","tid":2009674,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T02:35:00.000Z","msg":"陳茂波：若衝突持續將扼殺飲食業生存空間<br />\n10.05.2020 10:22<br />\n<br />\n財政司長陳茂波在網誌指，雖然疫情稍有紓緩，但近日再出現人群聚集與衝突，干擾商店商場的營運環境。他指本港食肆總收益數字，自去年4月開始持續萎縮，跌幅由不足1%逐步擴大到今年首季的32%。今年二月份的食肆總收益只有58億元，只等於去年同期的五成八。如果衝突持續，將扼殺這些行業的生存空間。他呼籲即使持不同的意見，也應該堅守和平原則。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1286432&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1286432%26csid%3D261_341&d=EEWyN02WlTtsLATURr%2FfpaVNHo2TAuuzEKoC36QvVjA%3D&h=52227508\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1286432&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"272019627189ffd796f5cb96c2f583d9e471db33","tid":2009674,"uid":56698,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T02:39:12.000Z","msg":"好鍾意樓主啲翻譯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>本港食肆總收益數字，自去年4月開始持續萎縮</blockquote><br />\n根本本身經濟本來就係唔掂，以前新市鎮區平日人流可以去到10點幾，2019年示威未起嘅時候已經提早，去到武漢肺炎時期8點未夠條街就無晒人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0678cb1743dfb7832816b4ad791db5f42e2cc23c","tid":2009674,"uid":181789,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T02:44:07.000Z","msg":"你有邊日唔會打壓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef03c93a42470fa1a2c5badff7b19f38b0c74970","tid":2009674,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T02:45:33.000Z","msg":"唔派黑警打壓香港經濟咪得"},{"pid":"6b75b5429647d949cd237b9d92ac1d0f403674d9","tid":2009674,"uid":127494,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"c